### Login with Alice
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### Create a new game for Section 6 testing
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games

### Get the created game
### Replace 3 with the new game id returned above
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/4

### Get planning data for the created game
### Replace 3 with the new game id returned above
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/4/planning

### Submit invalid route - empty route
### Replace 3 with the new game id returned above
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games/4/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segments": []
}

### Get game after invalid route
### finalScore should be 0
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/4

### Get steps after invalid route
### should return []
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/4/steps

### Create another game for valid route testing
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games

### Submit valid route
### Replace 4 with the new game id.
### Replace the segment ids with a real valid route from planning data.
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games/4/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segments": [18, 12, 3, 4]
}

### Get game after valid route
### finalScore should be updated
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/8

### Get steps after valid route
### should return one game_step per submitted segment
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/8/steps

### Try submitting the same completed game again
### should return 409 because game is no longer in planning
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games/8/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segments": [18, 12, 3, 4]  
}

### Invalid request body
### should return 422 because segments is not an array
POST http://localhost:3001/api/games/8/route
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segments": "wrong"
}

